description:
Insect warfare begins in a variety of forests, deserts, and waterfront locations.
Confront and defeat hostile insects, and add them to your army to expand your power.
The insect that builds the largest army wins!

Beetles, stag beetles, and butterflies of all kinds are here!
Determine which ones you are good at and which ones you are bad at, and use them to your advantage.
name: Attack on Beetle
intro:
The beetles begin their march!
Lead the horde to the top of the insects!
